column5: Hi Just wondering if you could give me some details as to size, number and location of fish you caught. We are leaving Thursday morning and can not wait. Any other advice would be appreciated.

we fished in the main lake straight out fromthe camp about 2 miles on a rock reef and thats were we caught most of our fish. also by the rapids was good we didnt catch any reel large fish but we sure caught alot of fish and had a great time great boats and motors youl will have a great time and good luck

Thanks.Just a couple of more questions. We are staying at the west cabin. Is this near your reef? What did you use? Any northerns? Size? About how many fish did you catch in a given day? Walleye size?Thanks again.
